title: Powerplant perform "Hey Mr. Dogman!" and more Live on KEXP

description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Powerplant performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded July 16, 2024.

Songs:
Hey Mr Dogman! 00:30
Bridge Of Sacrifice 03:13
Dog Is Seeing Ghosts Again/Dungen 06:54
Grass 11:44
Beautiful Boy 14:39

Theo Zhykharyev - Vocals, Guitar
Cam Pickering - Synth, Sampler
Karim Newble - Bass 
Joe McMahon - Drums

Host: Jennifer Govola
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering Engineer: Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
